Class BaseToscaElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentosca.toscana.model.BaseToscaElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class BaseToscaElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides means to access the data of the attached MappingEntity in a type-safe but generic way.
